{"tid":1288100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【皇上，小心呀】不嬲都係党指揮槍，而家香港地，槍想指揮党喎","createTime":"2019-07-05T13:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T14:11:04.000Z","uid":54337,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"226fed8f6ed061de50e862244622ba625c1f7198","tid":1288100,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:02:54.000Z","msg":"香港地，某某組織，有槍，最近完全失控，大膽越權，擅自搞外交。<br />\n不嬲都係党指揮槍，但而家槍想指揮党喎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n皇上，<br />\n香港的某某持槍組織，圖謀不軌，企圖顛覆国家，篡党奪權。<br />\n本人心繫偉大的祖国。<br />\n故此在連登，上書皇上。<br />\n望皇上明察呀。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a56a2cdeac6e85f7db6a07662da0fe88b97c6c","tid":1288100,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:09:03.000Z","msg":"黑警搞港獨軍政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50fd9f2c37e3cc10875dcbc436628c89c29867d2","tid":1288100,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:30:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://s1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/005xhfUQgy6WDkYWjPW10&amp;690\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs1.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F005xhfUQgy6WDkYWjPW10%26690&h=2091c6d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.71.cn/2013/0730/1375167052962.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.71.cn%2F2013%2F0730%2F1375167052962.png&h=0a920